snippet.title: Hamenos - Free Sci-Fi Browser MMO Game: October 2023
snippet.description:
Is it ready - NO! Is it playable now - YES! Is it fun - MAYBE! :)

Help me finish this game: 
Play now: https://hamenos.com/play.html
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/AvWNBF4nX8

Got a potato GPU? - I got ya! All you need is your mouse and your browser!

Dive into Hamenos, the creation of a passionate solo game developer. Crafted for massive PvP battles, envision epic space clashes with thousands in the vastness of the space – yes, you read that right: 1000v1000+ space PvP battles await! Launch straight into the action from your browser (recommended: Google Chrome). As I fine-tune the mechanics, I'm trying to ensure that player skills come first.

Song: NightMusicCup - Hamenos
Music provided by ... me :)
Watch: http://youtu.be/ya0o_KQ2gsI
